## [](#header-2).getEl()

Returns an element from page.

**Syntax**
```js
.getEl(selector, callback/*optional*/);
```

**Example**
```js
.getEl(".dropdown-link .user-name", function(element){
  console.log(element);
  // will print out {'ELEMENT': 1}
});
```

